<title>Prototype</title>
<para><literallayout><computeroutput>int&#32;set_tag(const&#32;char*&#32;tag_name,&#32;uint8_t&#32;n_bit);
</computeroutput></literallayout></para>
</section>
<section xml:id="_md__c_1_2programation_2ulaval_2_g_a_u_l_2programmation_2_t_a_g_c_a_n_2guide__utilisation_202___g_e_s_t_i_o_n___t_a_g_s_1autotoc_md42">
